title: Definitions
context: [ยง304A-3201.5] Definitions. As used in this subpart, unless the context clearly requires otherwise: &ldquo;Commission&rdquo; means the Western Interstate Commission for Higher Education. &ldquo;Hawaii commission&rdquo; means the Hawaii western interstate commission for higher education established under section 304A-3201.6. &ldquo;Hawaii commissioners&rdquo; means the members of the Hawaii western interstate commission for higher education.
